Our goal is to show:
`riemannZeta.zeroes_sum Set.univ (Set.Ioo 0 V) (fun ρ ↦ 1 / ρ.im) < FKS.Inputs.S₀ I + FKS.Inputs.B₁ I (FKS.Inputs.T₀ I) V`

Looking at the context, we have:
