Now we need to show that $\sum_{0 < \gamma < V} 1/\gamma < \sum_{0 < \gamma < I.T_0 + (V - I.T_0)} 1/\gamma$. This is true because $V > I.T_0$ and the sum is over an increasing interval.

```tactics
