  riemannZeta.zeroes_sum Set.univ (Set.Ioo 0 (I.T₀ + (V - I.T₀))) (fun ρ ↦ 1 / ρ.im) := by
  congr
  all_goals
    ext ρ
    simp
    <;> nlinarith
```

Next, we apply `lemma_2_1` to the interval $[I.T_0, I.T_0 + (V - I.T_0)]$ to get $\sum_{I.T_0 < \gamma < I.T_0 + (V - I.T_0)} 1/\gamma \leq B_1(I.T_0, I.T_0 + (V - I.T_0))$.

```tactics
