  riemannZeta.zeroes_sum Set.univ (Set.Ioo 0 I.T₀) (fun ρ ↦ 1 / ρ.im) + 
  riemannZeta.zeroes_sum Set.univ (Set.Ioo (I.T₀) (I.T₀ + (V - I.T₀))) (fun ρ ↦ 1 / ρ.im) := by
  rw [← Finset.sum_union (by 
    ext x
    simp
    <;> nlinarith
  )]
  <;> ring_nf
  <;> simp
  <;> ring
```

