```tactics
have h5 : riemannZeta.zeroes_sum Set.univ (Set.Ioo 0 (I.T₀ + (V - I.T₀))) (fun ρ ↦ 1 / ρ.im) < I.S₀ + I.B₁ I.T₀ (I.T₀ + (V - I.T₀)) := by
  linarith [h1, h3, h4]
```

Finally, we rewrite $I.T_0 + (V - I.T_0) = V$ to get the final result:

```tactics
rw [show I.T₀ + (V - I.T₀) = V by linarith] at h2 h5
linarith [h2, h5]
